# 👨‍💼 Employee CRUD System

A full-stack web application to manage employee records efficiently. Built with a Java backend and a dynamic JavaScript frontend, this system allows users to perform all essential Create, Read, Update, and Delete (CRUD) operations on employee data.

---

## 🚀 Features

- ➕ Add new employee records
- 📋 View list of all employees
- ✏️ Update existing employee details
- 🗑️ Delete employee records
- 🔗 RESTful API integration between frontend and backend
- 📱 Clean and responsive user interface

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

**Backend:**
- Java
- Spring Boot
- REST APIs

**Frontend:**
- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript

---

## 📁 Project Structure

```
Employee-Crud-system/
├── Backend/        # Java Spring Boot REST API
├── Frontend/       # HTML, CSS, JavaScript UI
└── README.md
```

---

## ⚙️ Getting Started

### Prerequisites
- Java 17+
- Node.js (for frontend, if applicable)
- MySQL or any relational database
- IntelliJ IDEA / VS Code

### Backend Setup
```bash
cd Backend
# Configure your database in application.properties
./mvnw spring-boot:run
```

### Frontend Setup
```bash
cd Frontend
# Open index.html in your browser
# OR use Live Server in VS Code
```

